Description: It's time once again for my annual holiday guitar sale. Lot's of people look forward to this each year, so here we go. You are looking at an American made Fender USA '52 Reissue Telecaster Thin Skin electric guitar, that comes with the original Fender Custom Shop black hard shell case with black plush velvet interior. The guitar is in excellent condition, and just has 1 chip in the transparent red finish. Other than that, the body looks very nice and just has a few marks on the rear from playing, and very light marks on the pick guard. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a cool and collectible guitar, that is sure to keep going up in value. Each year I sell off the high end guitars that we have acquired at our pawn shop during the year, and they have been sold to almost every country in the world. We only sell quality products, and our feedback will back that up. All will be sold on a no reserve basis, and no auctions will be closed early or with a buy it now, so bid to buy. Thanks for looking, and please check out my other auctions too. On Dec-19-18 at 14:12:18 PST, seller added the following information: The serial number is 74805.
Title: Fender USA Telecaster Thin Skin in transparent red with original hard shell case
